front.title: •Sebulba (V) (AI)
front.gametext: Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Deploys free to Mos Espa. While on Tatooine, attrition against opponent is +1 here and your Force generation is +1. When You're A Slave? places a card in your Used Pile, may draw top card of your Reserve Deck.
front.lore: Bad tempered Dug from Pixelito. He was about to turn Jar Jar into orange goo, until Anakin intervened.
